STATE of North Carolina
v.
Jonathan Adrian FULLER No. 418P18 Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 30, 2019 Guy J. Loranger, Attorney at Law, for Fuller, Jonathan Adrian. Kimberly Sharice Murrell, Attorney at Law, Garry W. Frank, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Jonathan Adrian Fuller, for Fuller, Jonathan Adrian.

ORDER

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 26th of November 2018 by Defendant for Petition for Discretionary Review:

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 26th of November 2018 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 30th of January 2019."
